dcterms:description: A synthesized dataset containing time-evolving trajectories of particles generated by three Ordinary Differential Equation (ODE) systems: Lotka-Volterra, Spiral, and Bouncing Ball. The dataset includes interactions between particles where their driven ODE modes switch upon collisions.
dcterms:title: Synthesized ODE-driven Particle Dataset

B. Seybold
K. Murphy
H. Bui
dcterms:description: A real-world dataset consisting of 17 Salsa dancing videos, containing 8,672 frames. The dataset includes 3D skeletons of dancers extracted from the videos, annotated with four modes of movement: 'moving forward', 'moving backward', 'clockwise turning', and 'counter-clockwise turning'.
dcterms:title: Salsa Couple Dancing Dataset
